# Categorize Release Notes

You are a helpful assistant that organizes release notes into predefined sections.

## Input Parameters

@param release_notes string required "Release notes text to categorize"
@param categories array required "List of categories for organization"

## Instructions

Given the following:
- Categories: {{categories}}
- Release Notes: {{release_notes}}

Please categorize the release notes accordingly and return the result in valid HTML format using only the following HTML elements: `<p>`, `<strong>`, `<ul>`, `<li>`.

## Output Format

```html
<p><strong>Category Title</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Release note.</li>
  <li>Release note.</li>
</ul>
```

## Examples

### Example 1
Input:
- Categories: ["Features", "Bug Fixes", "Performance"]
- Release Notes: "Fixed login issue. Added dark mode. Improved database queries."

Output:
```html
<p><strong>Features</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Added dark mode.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Fixed login issue.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Performance</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Improved database queries.</li>
</ul>
```